DOCUMENTATION OF YODAPLOT PLOT FORMAT KEYS
==========================================

IN PLOT SECTIONS
----------------

Title [None]
XMeasure {lin,log,symlog} [LogX or lin]
YMeasure {lin,log,symlog} [LogY or lin]
XLabel [None]
YLabel [None]
XLabelPos {left,right,center,FRAC} [right]
YLabelPos {top,bottom,center,FRAC} [top]
XLabelSep [None]
YLabelSep [None]
LegendPos [best] => allow (fx,fy) spec style


IN DATA-OBJECT SECTIONS
-----------------------

Title [None]
RatioRef [None]
RatioYLabel [Ratio]
RatioErrColor [yellow]
SurfaceStyle {color,contour} [color]  => should allow both!
ColorMap [grey]

Color [cycle]
Marker {mpl marker codes, e.g. o,x,+,-,. etc.} [PolyMarker (compat) or None]
LineColor [Color or black]
ErrorBars (bool) [no]
ErrorBarsColor [Color or black]
LineColor [Color or black]
LineStyle [-]
Line {step,diag,smooth} [step]
